+
+## Constraints
+
+- Do not reopen broad mission planning.
+- Do not start the Step-5 repair pass itself.
+- Keep the final verdict inside the Step-4 buckets:
+  `survives`,
+  `fails`,
+  or
+  `remains ambiguous`,
+  with one named reason each.
