+| `F_BM` | anti-circuit | exact Beltrami-aligned role packet with mandatory mirror completion; same-helicity alignment is frozen before outcomes; the exact nonlinear forcing ledger is static so `int_I D_on = 0` | `Beltrami cancellation`, `mirror-mode completion` |
