+# Exploration 003 Report - Pro-Circuit Dossier And Step-5 Readiness Verdict
+
+## Goal
+
+Apply the same frozen Step-4 burden currency to the pro-circuit families:
+
+- `F_SS(mu)`:
+  engineered-sign / sparse-triad family
+- `F_SL(rho)`:
+  scale-separated / dynamically-negligible-leakage family
+
+Then compare those outcomes against the anti-circuit dossier and decide whether
+Chain Step 5 is now well posed as one honest repair pass.
+
