+
+## Method
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Keep the same normalized window `I = [0, 1]`, the same packet
+  object, and the same thresholds from `exploration-001`.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Compare pro-circuit outcomes against the anti-circuit dossier
