+
+## Constraints
+
+- Do not run the anti-circuit or pro-circuit outcome comparison yet.
+- Do not import Tao's averaged freedoms by hand.
+- Do not change the forced spectator partition
+  `mirror`,
+  `companion`,
+  `feedback`,
+  `cross`.
+- Do not write a soft aggregate score.
+
